author: @Datenmeer
content: She doesn't have a live band or backup singers so the backup voice is pre-recorded (instead of backup singers) and she sings the chorus together with it. At 1:14 when the verses start you can see that it's not lip-syched. However she fully lip-synchs "Erotica" and "Justify my Love" - probably because it's mainly spoken.
